{"type":"message","id":"d2ae6887","parentId":"d764a694","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:13:19.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API returned an access denied error, indicating that the app doesn't have the required wiki permissions. The error message is clear: the app needs to apply for wiki:wiki, wiki:wiki:readonly, or wiki:node:read permissions.\n\nI should let the user know that the document cannot be accessed because the app is missing the required permissions.\n","thinkingSignature":"a8834a4ef26abc25ed49453954eb6bb2a9cc9045b867ff7ac888fc93d05ff86c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n<final>\n**打不开** ❌\n\n缺少 `wiki:wiki` 权限。需要在飞书开放平台开通：\n\n👉 **申请链接**：https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93202000f399bde/auth?q=wiki:wiki,wiki:wiki:readonly,wiki:node:read\n\n开通后就可以读取这个知识库文档了。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":494,"output":153,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20615,"cost":{"input":0.0001482,"output":0.0001836,"cacheRead":0.0005990399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009308399999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774836794383,"responseId":"06190f3a51980d74292942723550b41e"}}
