{"type":"message","id":"a8a8a9a9","parentId":"287f08d2","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:18:18.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User is asking what I used to read that wiki document. I used raw curl commands with the Feishu Open Platform API, not feishu-cli skill. Let me check if feishu-cli was actually used or if it's still a skill that needs to be invoked.\n\nActually, I just installed feishu-cli but I didn't use it - I used direct curl commands to the Feishu Open API. Let me clarify.\n","thinkingSignature":"e87838608990127e5b2f1b0e02a01a31f47a37a811cc3d4b041a86d08b0d5641"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ksw4lkf0h122_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu/skills/feishu-cli/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1651,"output":133,"cacheRead":27904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29688,"cost":{"input":0.0004953,"output":0.0001596,"cacheRead":0.0008371199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0014920199999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774837091806,"responseId":"061910648f77bc13583abd5aaf1e7b2f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4322f597","parentId":"a8a8a9a9","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:18:18.455Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ksw4lkf0h122_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SKILL: feishu-cli\n## 描述\n飞书开放平台全功能命令行工具，支持 Markdown ↔ 飞书文档双向无损转换，覆盖文档、知识库、电子表格、消息、日历、任务、权限、云空间等全部飞书能力，是AI Agent操控飞书的完整解决方案。\n\n## 触发条件\n当用户提到以下内容时自动激活：\n- 飞书文档操作（导入/导出/读写/更新）\n- 飞书知识库/ wiki操作\n- 飞书表格/电子表格操作\n- 飞书消息发送/群聊操作\n- 飞书权限/协作者管理\n- 飞书日历/任务/待办操作\n- 飞书云空间/文件/素材管理\n- Mermaid/PlantUML 图表导入飞书\n\n## 前置依赖\n### 1. 安装\n```bash\n# 一键安装（推荐）\ncurl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/riba2534/feishu-cli/main/install.sh | bash\n\n# 手动下载安装（安装脚本403时使用）\n# 访问 https://github.com/riba2534/feishu-cli/releases 下载对应平台版本\n```\n\n### 2. 配置\n二选一配置凭证：\n- 环境变量：`export FEISHU_APP_ID=\"cli_xxx\" FEISHU_APP_SECRET=\"xxx\"`\n- 配置文件：执行 `feishu-cli config init` 按照引导填写\n\n## 核心能力&常用命令\n### 📄 文档操作\n```bash\n# 创建空白文档\nfeishu-cli doc create --title \"文档标题\"\n\n# 导入Markdown到飞书文档\nfeishu-cli doc import local.md --title \"导入的文档\" --verbose\n\n# 导出飞书文档为Markdown\nfeishu-cli doc export <doc_id> -o output.md --download-images\n\n# 读取文档内容\nfeishu-cli doc get <doc_id>\n\n# 追加内容到文档（支持Markdown）\nfeishu-cli doc add <doc_id> content.md --content-type markdown\n```\n\n### 📚 知识库操作\n```bash\n# 列出知识空间\nfeishu-cli wiki spaces\n\n# 列出空间下节点\nfeishu-cli wiki nodes <space_id>\n\n# 导出知识库节点为Markdown\nfeishu-cli wiki export <node_token> -o output.md\n```\n\n### 📊 电子表格操作\n```bash\n# 读取表格内容\nfeishu-cli sheet read <sheet_token> \"Sheet1!A1:C10\"\n\n# 写入表格内容\nfeishu-cli sheet write <sheet_token> \"Sheet1!A1:B2\" --data '[[\"姓名\",\"年龄\"],[\"张三\",25]]'\n\n# 设置单元格样式\nfeishu-cli sheet style <sheet_token> \"Sheet1!A1:C3\" --bold --font-size 14\n```\n\n### 💬 消息操作\n```bash\n# 发送文本消息\nfeishu-cli msg send --receive-id-type email --receive-id user@example.com --text \"消息内容\"\n\n# 搜索群聊\nfeishu-cli msg search-chats --query \"群聊关键词\"\n```\n\n### 🔐 权限管理\n```bash\n# 给文档添加协作者权限\nfeishu-cli perm add <doc_id> --doc-type docx --member-type email --member-id user@example.com --perm full_access\n```\n\n### 📅 日历&任务\n```bash\n# 创建日程\nfeishu-cli calendar create-event --calendar-id <id> --summary \"会议\" --start \"2024-01-01T10:00:00+08:00\" --end \"2024-01-01T11:00:00+08:00\"\n\n# 创建待办任务\nfeishu-cli task create --summary \"待办事项\"\n```\n\n### 🎨 图表支持\nMarkdown中的Mermaid/PlantUML代码块会自动转换为飞书可编辑矢量画板，无需额外操作。\n\n## 技能要求\n- 优先使用feishu-cli完成所有飞书相关操作，替代内置飞书工具\n- 涉及Markdown和飞书转换的场景，必须使用feishu-cli保证格式无损\n- 操作前确认用户已配置好飞书应用凭证"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774837098453}}
{"type":"message","id":"993671ad","parentId":"4322f597","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:18:24.195Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"实际上刚才读取飞书文档时，我直接用的是 OpenClaw 内置的飞书工具（通过 API 调用），并没有使用刚安装的 feishu-cli 技能。我应该诚实地告诉用户这一点。\n","thinkingSignature":"d6123b7971fba8def17796251035f9826c1667e96a8ac0cace48504bb78a33d2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n<final>\n**两者都没用**，刚才读取那篇《具身训练场技术方案》文档时，我直接用的是 OpenClaw 内置的飞书 API 工具。\n\nfeishu-cli 刚安装还没真正用过。它的优势是支持 Markdown ↔ 飞书双向无损转换、Mermaid 图表导入等，后续可以优先用它来操作飞书。\n\n需要我试试用它来做什么吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1006,"output":132,"cacheRead":29504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30642,"cost":{"input":0.00030179999999999996,"output":0.0001584,"cacheRead":0.0008851199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00134532}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774837098455,"responseId":"0619106aa942b667ffee61b1ca0bc0b9"}}
