{"type":"message","id":"9e34e8a5","parentId":"7260a584","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:19:39.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what the built-in Feishu API tools are. I saw from the openclaw status output earlier that these plugins are registered: feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes, feishu_chat, feishu_wiki, feishu_drive, feishu_bitable. Let me check the available skills to see which ones are built-in vs installed.\n","thinkingSignature":"2ae96760e6ed2ec5a7eedcd7f70f1597ceca8095f7bbfff3e33d51c6c7541501"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j6vhfrenj3l4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1487,"output":131,"cacheRead":30464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32082,"cost":{"input":0.0004461,"output":0.0001572,"cacheRead":0.0009139199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00151722}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774837173918,"responseId":"061910b6f6c066ee5dfb425177005143"}}
{"type":"message","id":"54611fd8","parentId":"9e34e8a5","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:19:39.068Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_j6vhfrenj3l4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"feishu-doc\nfeishu-drive\nfeishu-perm\nfeishu-wiki"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"feishu-doc\nfeishu-drive\nfeishu-perm\nfeishu-wiki","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774837179064}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c176b03","parentId":"54611fd8","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:19:47.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me explain the built-in feishu tools from openclaw.\n","thinkingSignature":"7f378435822c5ade8fabc63d3c3ba393e4a45aa3956bb36799bcd64434eaebb7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n<final>\nOpenClaw 内置了 4 个飞书插件/技能：\n\n| 插件 | 功能 |\n|---|---|\n| **feishu-doc** | 文档读写、导入导出 |\n| **feishu-wiki** | 知识库节点管理 |\n| **feishu-drive** | 云空间文件管理 |\n| **feishu-perm** | 文档权限与协作者管理 |\n\n刚才读取那篇文档就是用的 `feishu-wiki`（获取节点）+ `feishu-doc raw_content`（获取内容）。\n\n这些插件随 OpenClaw 一起安装，算是\"内置\"的。而 `feishu-cli` 是从 ClawHub 额外安装的 CLI 工具，两者都可以操作飞书。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":97,"output":175,"cacheRead":31936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32208,"cost":{"input":0.0000291,"output":0.00020999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0009580799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00119718}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774837179069,"responseId":"061910bb4355991a31ad1fc6ccdda5fa"}}
